(Test G-code for Tangential Arcs)
G17 G21 G90 G54 (XY Plane, mm, Absolute, Coord System 1)
F1000           (Set a visible feedrate)

(Step 1: Straight move to establish initial heading)
G0 X0 Y0
G1 X10 Y0

(Step 2: G3 Counter-Clockwise Circle)
(Start: 10,0 | Center: 20,0 | End: 10,0)
G3 X10 Y0 I10 J0

(Step 3: Move to position for G2)
G1 X30 Y0

(Step 4: G2 Clockwise Circle)
(Start: 30,0 | Center: 40,0 | End: 30,0)
G2 X30 Y0 I10 J0

(Step 5: Return Home)
G1 X0 Y0
M2
